- L-I'm desperate here.
- Then I'll make you a deal.

16:44.136 --> 16:48.129
- I want you to throw the softball game.
- Never!

16:48.240 --> 16:50.902
- He gave me this.
- Course he did. Why do you think he hired you?

16:51.010 --> 16:53.877
He liked my ideas.

16:53.979 --> 16:55.879
They were my ideas,
and, no, he didn't.

16:55.981 --> 16:59.712
He wants you for the softball game because
he's trying to make our family look foolish.

16:59.818 --> 17:04.653
I knew you had bad ideas.
All right, we'll play <i>him.</i>

17:04.757 --> 17:07.385
I'll throw that softball game.

17:07.492 --> 17:10.723
Nobody makes a fool of
our family without my help.

17:17.102 --> 17:21.334
<i>[Narrator] Tobias had talked up the name</i>
<i>Fünke, and it was time to audition.</i>

17:21.440 --> 17:24.170
- What's your name?
- Tobias.

17:24.276 --> 17:26.300
He's too short. Give it to the guard.

17:26.412 --> 17:31.748
Oh. L- I'm not. L-
On camera, I seem much taller.

17:31.850 --> 17:35.149
<i>And Maeby picked up the reader's report,</i>
<i>which had now become her book report.</i>

17:35.254 --> 17:37.950
- Whatcha got there?
- I can't really discuss it.

17:38.057 --> 17:40.457
If you wanna get it made,
I'm the guy who has to see it.

17:40.559 --> 17:44.188
You're the Fünke everyone's talking about?
What are you, like, 15?

17:44.296 --> 17:48.164
- Marry me. [Chuckles]
- Everyone thinks I look young too.

17:48.267 --> 17:51.259
- So who are you thinking about?
- Jude Law. Why do you ask?

17:51.370 --> 17:53.838
Yeah. Go young <i>. Young Guy and the Sea.</i>
Big spring-breaker.

17:53.939 --> 17:56.931
Four C.G.I. The fish.
Let's fast-track this one.

